<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Over the past few months I have written a long=
 piece about crypto for Bloomberg Businessweek. It is out today, and <a hre=
f=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29487703.291504/aHR0cHM6=
